Gameplay and Design of Derby Dash

This thrilling online slot game has a high RTP of 96% and high variance. With 10 paylines across the five reels and four rows, you have the chance to win up to 1,000 times your bet. Features include nudges, free spins, multipliers, and wilds. Stakes range from €0.2 to €200.

Horse-Themed Symbols

Derby Dash Bonus Spins and Free Spins

Free Spins

Bucks Feature

In the world of Derby Dash, players can capture a special symbol that will randomly multiply their winnings by 2x to 10x. These symbols appear on 1 to 5 reels, with the highest multiplier only appearing on a single reel and the others offering slightly lower multipliers. Please note that the standard wild symbol does not apply to this feature.

Nudging Reels Feature

The Nudging Reels feature can be randomly activated, allowing for selected reels to move up to five positions to give players a winning combination.
